09:13.080 --> 09:14.620
Don't worry if this is difficult.

09:14.620 --> 09:15.699
i will find a way

09:15.699 --> 09:16.759
Help you achieve this goal

09:18.320 --> 09:19.424
I don't have any wishes

09:21.039 --> 09:22.140
how so?

09:22.140 --> 09:24.639
