to comfort his family.

13:13.080 --> 13:14.519
Incidentally,

13:14.519 --> 13:15.959
Department of Justice
and Department of Income and Population

13:15.959 --> 13:17.320
Efforts have been made
to catch the perpetrators, but without success.

