13:29.679 --> 13:31.100
It's the minister's job

13:31.100 --> 13:32.919
To relieve the emperor's worries.

13:34.519 --> 13:35.960
If possible, could you also try it?

13:35.960 --> 13:37.759
Recover misappropriated salt taxes?

13:38.559 --> 13:39.620
Then,

13:39.620 --> 13:41.159
