14:17.559 --> 14:19.840
The Salt Transportation Department
is the main tax department.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.759
The previous salt transport envoy
embezzled so much money.

14:23.840 --> 14:25.000
It seems I really need

14:25.000 --> 14:26.639
Consider candidates carefully.

14:32.440 --> 14:33.440
I thought General Yan’s second son,

14:33.440 --> 14:34.440
