14:45.300 --> 14:46.480
He should be entrusted with important tasks.

14:47.399 --> 14:49.919
I understand your Majesty's intention,

14:49.919 --> 14:52.320
I will consider it carefully.

14:54.279 --> 14:55.440
Hot water is coming.

