16:40.320 --> 16:41.680
When Master Rong woke up,

16:41.680 --> 16:43.080
He will definitely be hungry.

16:44.480 --> 16:45.504
OK

17:18.119 --> 17:19.240
Rigorous investigation is currently underway.

17:19.240 --> 17:20.539
