17:20.539 --> 17:21.640
Wait for my news

17:27.400 --> 17:28.448
How are you?

17:30.880 --> 17:31.936
I am fine.

17:33.240 --> 17:34.368
everything is fine.

17:34.880 --> 17:36.420
You always say that.

17:36.420 --> 17:37.960
It would be great if I knew martial arts

17:37.960 --> 17:39.799
I can protect you rain or shine.

17:41.759 --> 17:43.680
Everything you have done for me
is enough.

17:44.279 --> 17:46.039
