17:46.920 --> 17:48.500
When all this is done,

17:48.500 --> 17:49.536
We can do anything you want.

17:50.079 --> 17:51.680
I will support you no matter what,
even if it means risking my life.

17:52.960 --> 17:54.319
Don't say that.

17:55.039 --> 17:56.100
We all need to be safe and healthy.

17:56.100 --> 17:57.319
