20:10.799 --> 20:12.680
Now you and Master Rong

20:12.680 --> 20:14.319
Looks really in love.

20:14.319 --> 20:15.620
don't make fun of me

20:15.620 --> 20:17.160
related to this matter.

20:18.839 --> 20:20.680
He is just a child,

20:21.200 --> 20:22.240
