21:38.519 --> 21:40.960
And drag him down?

21:41.799 --> 21:43.480
But you are not that person.

21:44.240 --> 21:46.079
Who cares if you are?

21:47.880 --> 21:49.079
None of this matters.

21:50.000 --> 21:51.072
What's important is that

21:51.880 --> 21:52.920
you have to ask yourself

21:53.599 --> 21:55.319
Have you never liked Master Yung?

21:58.640 --> 22:00.200
I don't.

22:11.759 --> 22:12.896
